WEBVTT

00:00.560 --> 00:06.100
Utah inventor Paul Pantone has developed what he calls the Geet fuel processor,

00:06.700 --> 00:14.160
a plasma generator similar to a super carburetor that actually appears to run on 80% water and is entirely non-polluting.

00:15.080 --> 00:20.340
This device replaces the carburetor and exhaust and combines them as one unit,

00:21.740 --> 00:24.660
whereas this end of it acts as a miniature refinery,

00:24.660 --> 00:31.520
allowing the engine to run on everything from battery acid and water mix to crude oil right out of the ground.

00:31.520 --> 00:36.020
This is Angola crude, 39.5 gravity.

00:36.020 --> 00:55.800
The exhaust coming down goes around and comes out here at the far end.

00:55.800 --> 01:01.260
The center chamber draws some of the heat from the exhaust, plus this tube takes some

01:01.260 --> 01:07.740
the exhaust gases takes them up into the chamber and bubbles them down to the bottom the bubbles

01:07.740 --> 01:12.940
as it comes through the fuel are brought up to the top of the chamber picked up through a tube

01:12.940 --> 01:18.940
and fed up the center of the exhaust pipe while they're being fed up the exhaust pipe they are in

01:18.940 --> 01:27.260
a vacuum and there is a heat exchange which occurs this process has been argument argued a few times

01:27.260 --> 01:32.780
to be either a plasma field an electro field we do know that it does have a slight radiation which

01:32.780 --> 01:39.180
is not alpha beta or gamma and we do have x-rays to show that whatever is coming from the unit

01:39.180 --> 01:47.340
does get affected different from stainless steel than the regular steel

02:03.500 --> 02:07.580
when the temperature of the exhaust is the same as the air temperature going in

02:07.580 --> 02:15.820
from the air portion up here, normally 1, 3% more oxygen coming out of the tailpipe than there is in the air we're breathing.

02:18.500 --> 02:19.860
And no carbon at all.

02:20.020 --> 02:20.800
Carbon vanishes.

02:21.860 --> 02:26.040
I wouldn't say vanishes, I would say transmute it into some other substance, a lighter element,

02:26.500 --> 02:30.920
because we have an abundance of lighter elements here that are not explained from down here.

02:31.840 --> 02:35.560
But during the heat process, there are molecular changes.

02:35.560 --> 02:44.240
after running this engine from 1983 until now and many times we had it running eight eight eight and

02:44.240 --> 02:51.460
a half hours a day we have never had to change spark plug change the oil or clean it we have

02:51.460 --> 02:55.720
taken the head off three times to inspect the inside of it and it's been spotless

